PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (PART IV) to the extent of reinstating section 400.06 [Extension of Validity Period] and by enacting section 400.07, which obliges the holder of a permit or licence to notify the Department of Transport of any change in their permanent address within seven days.
